LTV (Pro): $12/mo × 12 months = $144/year (5–10x CAC)
LTV (Agency): $79/mo × 12 months = $948/year (50x+ CAC)
MRR grows as user base grows (recurring, not transactional)
Option B: Keep $12 Per-Use, But Add Recurring "Membership"
If you want to keep the pay-per-use model:

